targets.rawSql:
-- Time since in seconds
SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (NOW() - MAX(time))) AS seconds_since_last_action
FROM solar.bess1_metrics 
WHERE $__timeFilter("time") 
AND metric LIKE 'ACTION-%'

SELECT value, time, metric 
FROM solar.bess1_metrics 
WHERE $__timeFilter("time") 
AND metric LIKE 'AE-num_nan_obs'
ORDER BY "time"

SELECT value, time, metric 
FROM solar.bess1_metrics 
WHERE $__timeFilter("time") 
AND metric LIKE 'AE-imputed'
ORDER BY "time"

SELECT evaluator, (data->'x')::float as x, (data->'y')::float as y
FROM solar.bess1_evals, jsonb_array_elements(value->'data') as data
WHERE $__timeFilter("time") AND agent_step = (
  SELECT agent_step FROM solar.bess1_evals WHERE $__timeFilter(time) AND evaluator LIKE 'pdf%' ORDER BY time desc LIMIT 1
)
AND evaluator LIKE 'pdf%'
ORDER BY "time"

SELECT evaluator, (data->'x')::float as x, (data->'y')::float as y
FROM solar.bess1_evals, jsonb_array_elements(value->'data') as data
WHERE $__timeFilter("time") AND agent_step = (
  SELECT max(agent_step) FROM solar.bess1_evals WHERE $__timeFilter(time) AND evaluator LIKE 'qs%'
)
AND evaluator LIKE 'qs%'
ORDER BY "time"

AND metric LIKE 'ACTION-%'
OR metric LIKE 'RAW-ELS_SLR_BESS1_SOC'
